          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1708618428318-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>beef stock mix </strong>and<strong> tomato paste </strong>in 100ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> [170ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1708618432722-x200.jpg",
