          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1708618432722-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a little <strong>olive oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>pepper</strong> <strong>strips</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until charred and tender</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Cook half the pepper strips here and save the rest for later!</span></strong></p><p>Once done, transfer to a bowl and set aside, reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1708618437405-x200.jpg",
