            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the<strong> pork & beef taco mix</strong> equally between each warmed tortilla and top with the <strong>charred pepper & herb salsa</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave out the salsa and serve the reserved chopped tomato in the tacos with the reserved pepper strips to the side!</span></strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
